analysis: The agent included an unsupported parameter ("analysisDepth": 5) in the function call, resulting in no exact match with the expected function signature and causing the evaluator to not recognize the call.

The agent incorrectly formatted the "ageGroup" argument as a range (20-30) instead of a valid single value (e.g., 20), causing a JSON parsing error. It should have matched the expected parameter format for "ageGroup."

The agent omitted required parameters "serviceSectorGrowth" and "foreignInvestment" in the EconomicDevelopmentMetrics function call, providing only "industrialOutput" despite the user's request to focus on service sector growth and foreign investments.
The agent incorrectly set the "receptionDelay" parameter to 10 instead of the correct value of 1200, resulting in a function call that did not match the expected input and thus failed validation.
